{"tid":1871660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外資集團排隊派錢比支那，班官Fat Fat","createTime":"2020-02-09T15:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T08:18:28.000Z","uid":13355,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec3e06a10c6f5caf7483a99756f6f60c8ec3dc8","tid":1871660,"uid":13355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUO1mwA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUO1mwA.jpg&h=29eaf9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQQrxDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQQrxDg.jpg&h=c9c088be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ne-np.facebook.com/MingWatch/posts/1846914615433856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fne-np.facebook.com%2FMingWatch%2Fposts%2F1846914615433856%2F&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=eb6451c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ne-np.facebook.com/MingWatch/posts/1846914615433856/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【各大奢侈品集團捐款助抗疫】<br />\n<br />\nWARS疫情嚴峻，全球各大奢侈品集團先後捐出巨額予武漢及湖北紅十字會，全力資助中國大陸抗疫。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LVMH捐出約1,600萬人民幣，Kering開雲集團捐出750萬人民幣，Richemont歷峰集團亦宣布捐出1,000萬人民幣，美容品牌如L&rsquo;Or&eacute;al和Est&eacute;e Lauder亦分別捐出500萬及200萬人民幣。</span></span>LVMH集團更致力於法國及歐洲等地收集重要及緊缺物資送到內地，而上一次巴黎聖母院大火，LVMH反應亦相當迅速，率先捐款協助重建。"},{"pid":"7673a5fb5161880b3ef90445ff5e3dcea05a08e2","tid":1871660,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:09:24.000Z","msg":"捐俾火葬場？"},{"pid":"4035800b5f47b67fb45edd99d531c8bcc85401e0","tid":1871660,"uid":13355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"仲要比湖北紅十字會"},{"pid":"831d3f1ba7b4dc4e7cfcdedaeb4fdd979c06ef81","tid":1871660,"uid":13355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"幾個仆街集團，捐咁撚多錢，平時就剝削員工，一陣你信唔信仲栽員"},{"pid":"c6640b0be23fbd541fdf43